---
title: Roasted Eggplant Biryani with Currants & Almonds
description: Biryani – the fragrant rice dish hailing from the Indian subcontinent – gets a twist with this vegetarian version that uses cubes of roasted eggplant to add a ton of flavour, plus roasted almonds for crunch and a dollop of creamy Greek yoghurt to complement the mild spices.
